## Final Checklist

Before publishing a new rule file:

- [ ] Frontmatter includes description and globs
- [ ] Examples use generic domain names
- [ ] Code snippets are minimal and focused
- [ ] ✅/❌ patterns used consistently
- [ ] Includes "why" not just "what"
- [ ] Has decision tree or when-to-use guidance
- [ ] Cross-references related rules
- [ ] Exceptions and edge cases noted
- [ ] Easy to scan with clear hierarchy
- [ ] No project-specific examples
